Brynn Johnson and Cassie Miller were brought together by a terrible tragedy .
Cassie was in her car picking up Brynn 's younger daughter , 17-month-old Rowyn , who was killed .
Brynn forgave Cassie for what happened , acknowledging what happened as a horrific accident .
Rowyn was only 17-months-old when she was killed instantly in the driveway of her home in Tenino , Washington .